As part of growing engagement between Shanghai and 🇮🇳 metro cities 🌆, Consul General @PratikMathur1 was happy to welcome @Rotary Kilpauk, #Chennai members to Shanghai for an immersion tour and workshop in Eastern China.☀️🌼

➡️ In his remarks to the members, Consul General underlined the importance of growing people to people and #connectivity exchanges in strengthening our relations in sectors such as heritage tourism, cultural development and knowledge exchanges. As the fastest growing major economy and the youngest country on the planet, we remain confident and committed to #Global South development. 🪷🌾

➡️ In an engaging discussion, all participants agreed to work together to promote #greendevelopment, cultural cooperation and enhance mutual understanding and friendship. 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦💥💫

